message.content: The likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper are "cs.CL", "cs.AI", "cs.LG", "cs.NE", and "cs.IR". This is because the paper discusses a new version of the Stanford Question Answering Dataset (SQuAD) that includes unanswerable questions, which is relevant to natural language processing and machine learning (cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG). The paper also mentions the use of neural systems (cs.NE) and information retrieval (cs.IR) techniques.
